{"tid":2339158,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★中國版 App Store 疑受政治壓力 數千款遊戲年底前下架","createTime":"2020-12-24T12:12:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T12:17:56.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b127cf6c4b929a222550c70f0d5012bfc8c0807b","tid":2339158,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T12:12:34.000Z","msg":"【e-zone 專訊】蘋果（Apple）向來視中國為主要收入來源，亦一直大幅修改本身在國際市場的生態環境，以遷就此部分的生意。除了兩年因應內地法例，而於貴州設立中國專用 iCloud 數據中心外，早前蘋果中國版 App Store 也疑似受到政治壓力，而決定在 2020 年底前把數千款遊戲下架。<br />\n<br />\n在中國推出智能手機遊戲並不自由，於 4 年前起更需要取得官方許可，現時只有不足 100 個外國遊戲獲批准發行。不過，蘋果中國 App Store 一直能繞過此規定，開發者其實可推出遊戲產品。面對中國近年加強對互聯網的監管，早前就連旅遊資訊平台服務 Tripadvisor 也需要下架，遊戲部分也終於守不住。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2837125/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8BApp%20Store%E5%AF%A9%E6%9F%A5%20%20%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%E7%8B%82%E5%88%AA%E9%81%8E%E5%8D%83%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2837125%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258BApp%2520Store%25E5%25AF%25A9%25E6%259F%25A5%2520%2520%25E8%2598%258B%25E6%259E%259C%25E7%258B%2582%25E5%2588%25AA%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%258D%2583%25E9%2581%258A%25E6%2588%25B2&d=z%2FAKp4ZZwI77wMFl%2FSXGt04axDeVXns42j9POfnWuxs%3D&h=3e69298b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2837125/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8BApp%20Store%E5%AF%A9%E6%9F%A5%20%20%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%E7%8B%82%E5%88%AA%E9%81%8E%E5%8D%83%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2</a>"},{"pid":"abf2c4b3c62bdc723e39916a7da757cd54e44f52","tid":2339158,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T12:12:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac